This is an extension to [[rcirc]].

# Use /POUNCE to list the queues.
# Use /POUNCE NICK to list all messages queued for NICK
# Use /POUNCE NICK MESSAGE to add message to the queue for NICK
# Use /UNPOUNCE NICK to delete all messages queued for NICK

Source:

* Lisp:rcirc-pounce.el

To install, put it in your LoadPath and add the following to your InitFile:

    (eval-after-load 'rcirc '(require 'rcirc-pounce))

